Package: lan-clipboard-sync
Version: 0.1.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Your Name <your.email@example.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/zzttzzmyswy/lan-clipboard-sync
Description: A LAN clipboard synchronization tool
 A LAN clipboard synchronization tool supporting text, images, and files
 across Windows and Linux. This tool automatically syncs clipboard content
 between multiple devices on the same local network using encrypted
 communication.
 .
 Features:
  - Text, image, and file synchronization
  - End-to-end encryption using ChaCha20-Poly1305
  - Cross-platform support (Windows and Linux)
  - System tray integration for easy control
  - Configurable peers and file size limits